## Tiered Partnership Strategy

**Phase 1 — Affiliate Applications (NOW):** Online applications to affiliate networks. No calls needed. $50-100/funded account.
**Phase 2 — Activate + Optimize (500+ users):** Turn on affiliate links. Track conversion. A/B test placement.
**Phase 3 — Direct Partnerships (5K+ users):** Upgrade affiliates to direct deals. Negotiate 2-3x higher payouts.
**Phase 4 — Expand Categories (10K+ users):** Add lending, insurance, credit, B2B API partners.
**Phase 5 — B2B API Partners (Year 2+):** Formation API integrations for Distill. CPA association distribution for Distill SaaS.

